    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hm, that should indeed be made safe, however, how do you end up in a situation where `params` isn't in the result. Is it manually filtered out by you? If there's no `params`, I'm sure that the cache will not work. Safe solution would be bailing out of writing the cache altogether in that case.\r\n\r\nDo you have a reproducible example?",
