    "body": "Hi, could you verify that `params` is removed from the response fields in your index configuration? This should be under Configuration > Search behavior > Retrieved attributes:\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/assets/154633/465725f8-8193-46ae-a4b8-82cd71bd8627)\r\n\r\nOn our end we'll guard against this situation in an upcoming release of InstantSearch.",
